  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "A comment in `get_total_balance` reads that the function returns a minimum of 1 Gwei to avoid divisions by zero.\r\n\r\nBut since https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/1635, `total_balance` must be at least `EFFECTIVE_BALANCE_INCREMENT` in order to avoid a division by zero  in [this line](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blame/dev/specs/phase0/beacon-chain.md#L1369) of `get_attestation_deltas`:\r\n```\r\nrewards[index] = reward_numerator // (total_balance // increment)\r\n```\r\n\r\nIt seems that either the minimum of `total_balance` should be raised, or the reward calculation be adjusted to avoid this edge case.",
