    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "In a similar vein, if a slashed validators effective balance drops under EFFECTIVE_BALANCE_INCREMENT, it seems they will not suffer the anti-correlation penalty applied in `process_slashings`, as [the expression](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blame/dev/specs/phase0/beacon-chain.md#L1441):\r\n```\r\npenalty_numerator = validator.effective_balance // increment * min(sum(state.slashings) * 3, total_balance)\r\n```\r\nwill evaluate to 0.",
