    "body": "Right. The only way their effective balance could drop below `EFFECTIVE_BALANCE_INCREMENT` is if it went to 0 (because effective balance is only changed on that increment) which would give them zero penalty regardless.\r\n\r\nThat said, maybe `penalty_numerator` here should be in terms of `balance` rather than `effective_balance`",
